### 1. [medium] Test #13 does not add the claimed new failure-mode coverage
Refs: [scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-20260524T204950Z/scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh:87), [scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-20260524T204950Z/scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh:273), [scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-20260524T204950Z/scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh:291), [scripts/set-version.sh](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-20260524T204950Z/scripts/set-version.sh:331), [scripts/set-version.sh](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-20260524T204950Z/scripts/set-version.sh:377), [dev/plans/runs/0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-output.json](/tmp/fdb-0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-20260524T204950Z/dev/plans/runs/0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-output.json:15)

